  "Name": "BOX_PACK_REVERSAL",
  "Description": "BOX_PACK_REVERSAL\n\nThis process is used to reverse the pack of a MasterItem from a carrying entity. It will unpack all of the specified MasterItem from the specified carrying entity. It does not allow for a unpacking a specific quantity.\n\nThis process writes a new transaction of type UNPACK and sets the reversal ID of the original pack transaction. It will also update the packed quantity on the document detail line.",
